{"type":"markdown","params":{"markdown":"### Data will only be visible in this dashboard if you enable the IdentifyIngressEgressLateralTraffic system rule.    
* **Egress** traffic has a source IP in the internal network and a destination IP outside of your network.   
* **Ingress** traffic has a source IP that is outside your internal network and a destination IP that is inside your network.  
* **Lateral** traffic has  source and destination IPs inside your network.  
* **Other** trafic has no IP addresses or has IPV6 addresses.

Your internal network is defined by the IP ranges in the  IdentifyIngressEgressLateralTraffic system rule."},"aggs":[],"listeners":{}}
